title: Week 8: Friday Night Recap/Scores/Highlights
text:

1. Cleveland - Defeated Santa Fe 57-0 Cleveland is now 7-0, 1-0 in District Santa Fe is now 0-8, 0-2 in District

3. Centennial - Defeated Chaparral 49-3 Centennial is now 7-0, 2-0 in District Chaparral is now 5-2, 1-1 in District
